          <li><strong>AI Solutions:</strong> Building intelligent systems for automation, customer support, and business processes using cutting-edge AI technologies.</li>
          <li><strong>Space Tech Innovation:</strong> Exploring how AI and deep tech can contribute to space exploration and cosmic research.</li>
          <li><strong>Deep Tech Integration:</strong> Combining AI, quantum computing, and other advanced technologies for breakthrough solutions.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          Ready to explore the future of AI and space technology?
        </p>
        <div style={{ textAlign: "center" }}>
          <a
            href="/contact/"
            class="btn"
            style={{ fontSize: "larger", marginBottom: "4em" }}
          >
            Let's Connect & Collaborate
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <h2 class={style.subHeading}>
        <span>Recent posts</span>
      </h2>
      <div class={style.gridList}>
        {
          fdata.map((node) => (
            <Entry
              title={node.data.title}
              date={node.data.date.toString()}
              path={"/" + node.collection + "/" + node.slug}
              timeToRead={readingTime(node.body)}
              excerpt={node.data.excerpt}
              tags={node.data.tags}
            />
          ))
        }
      </div>

      <h2 class={style.subHeading}>
        <span>Featured articles</span>
      </h2>
      <div class={style.gridList}>
        {
          data.map((node) => (
            <Entry
              title={node.data.title}
              date={node.data.date.toString()}
              path={"/" + node.collection + "/" + node.slug}
              timeToRead={readingTime(node.body)}
              excerpt={node.data.excerpt}
              tags={node.data.tags}
            />
          ))
        }
      </div>

      <h2 class={style.subHeading}>
        <span>Explore more on this site</span>
      </h2>
      <div>
        <ul class={`${style.gridListExpanded} ${style.navList}`}>
          <li id="articles">
            <Entry
              key="articles-home-link"
